830ba.gif&h=56391f44&s={SIZE}\" />因為好似落雪咁 毛雪啊屌你<br />\n每日都要吸毛梳毛同佢玩 活動量好大<br />\n每日跑嚟跑去<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/030053_5ff74cc43784f430563172a0ca5c8934.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F030053_5ff74cc43784f430563172a0ca5c8934.gif&h=4d61bede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n性格硬頸 要好有耐性教<br />\n佢得閒又會鳩叫下 <br />\n仲有 有定心理準備買過哂啲家俬<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/025952_5b5e715a2ac4f882936f995c73e4083d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F025952_5b5e715a2ac4f882936f995c73e4083d.gif&h=c949d553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我嗰隻已經慣咗香港天氣 唔使成日開冷氣都得<br />\n佢熱得濟會叫人開冷氣 基本上平時有把風扇佢就舒服<br />\n有時仲怕凍要com被"},{"pid":"d36711e9fd8a611c209a52dca36a5b1542917c43","tid":1959580,"uid":149266,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"沖涼吹毛吹死你<br />\n佢面頭一層毛，底果層密到仆街，極難乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梳化 準備好換兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所有靚袋 鞋 記住收好<br />\n野食唔好周圍放 佢會摛到上枱咬走<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係 去做gym<br />\n因為雪橇狗衝撲去你度 係好撚痛喎重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你可以日日帶佢去街"},{"pid":"4368bca23c3577898b3b20da25bd1da10fe091e1","tid":1959580,"uid":149266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖涼吹毛吹死你<br />\n佢面頭一層毛，底果層密到仆街，極難乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梳化 準備好換兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所有靚袋 鞋 記住收好<br />\n野食唔好周圍放 佢會摛到上枱咬走<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係 去做gym<br />\n因為雪橇狗衝撲去你度 係好撚痛同重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你可以日日帶佢去街</blockquote>"},{"pid":"28bcc4232c3d4c491fe59e358770d66b5ebc8923","tid":1959580,"uid":1402,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":