 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你可以日日帶佢去街</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"日日帶佢落街係基本啦, 最好一日兩次<br />\n我相信放夠電應該屋企sofa都換少幾張"},{"pid":"371e2772aab384b867de3800af62c40cac1557d9","tid":1959580,"uid":313546,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"c70d700b1baaf7960ef447e8e3dafe82a63bceab","tid":1959580,"uid":40272,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"以前不嬲叫開雪橇 <br />\n係咪大陸先叫哈奇士？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔好咩9野都話係蝗語好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a92b6b945889c156fa00ea0cc7af90b6508e757","tid":1959580,"uid":313546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"你唔想虐待佢就預日日要開冷氣<br />\n同埋佢真係onon99咁 隨時跟左陌生人走都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745ef42968718541c11ce7b0072f1a987e443d36","tid":1959580,"uid":40272,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"371e2772aab384b867de3800af62c40cac1557d9","tid":1959580,"uid":313546,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"c70d700b1baaf7960ef447e8e3dafe82a63bceab","tid":1959580,"uid":40272,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"以前不嬲叫開雪橇 <br />\n係咪大陸先叫哈奇士？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔好咩9野都話係蝗語好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"以前真係叫雪橇喎 近一兩年先叫咩哈士奇"},{"pid":"d4bcf191ff3cafdc620240091dc79ce625619382","tid":1959580,"uid":333589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d33a3b9b2389de9b1968203a4e00077fb901a90","tid":1959580,"uid":150588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c83ef404f965b8070cda9ba83709406a9c9ecbd","tid":1959580,"uid":31151,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"c70d700b1baaf7960ef447e8e3dafe82a63bceab","tid":1959580