mal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"睇開嘅youtuber有養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9560aa26c7e28d389614c88cc15f31e0416f1430","tid":1959580,"uid":155853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2a2c8c6f3397edb40705bd95d2f3249fd73bc785","tid":1959580,"uid":77115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41afc385e0286eb5263d80ea9ce1abba455d9ad2","tid":1959580,"uid":155853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c7d1068319f79d681056f07f82f8bc36e1c5cfbb","tid":1959580,"uid":333589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"有冇方法應對定準備定銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"養西摩，兩年換過兩次梳化，雪橇應該都差無兩幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"想養西摩<br />\n係咪要外國買先健康<br />\n本地既西摩狗舍/breeder有冇邊間有保證（對啲狗好 唔會亂咁黎既）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"冇深究，我同老婆拍拖嗰陣已經傾過話第時想養西摩，有時得閒就周圍行下寵物店睇下狗bb，本身老婆好鍾意狗，佢以前都養過兩隻細狗<br />\n睇咗好多次都係得個睇字，冇刻意為買而買，結婚後第一個情人節咁啱又去勝利道行街睇狗仔，就撞到而家隻衰仔帶埋佢返屋企啦，2個半月返嚟而家2歲幾，托賴除咗西摩本身嘅腸胃問題外其他方面都好健康<br />\n另外識兩個西摩狗主一個係狗場搵嘅，另一個係接咗隻比人棄養嘅，兩隻都係健健康康冇乜問題，所以我覺得都係睇彩數，最重要係養得佢就好好照顧佢一世，絕對唔好因一時衝動最後棄養，由其養大狗係會更加勞心勞力"},{"pid":"c29c24879f21d4f5eb93ec095bfc93e0696aaa9c","tid":1959580,"uid":204634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T21:52:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B-olAM2RVF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB-olAM2RVF4&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=727b6ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B-olAM2RVF4</a>"},{"pid":"f5a4c924ef4e018a3c8d28ae10cb85eec3a525c8","tid":1959580,"uid":150588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c29c24879f21d4f5eb93ec095bfc93e0696aaa9c","tid":1959580,"uid":204634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy